                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-42-defend505 t17910413-42-punish239"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
